xxl.core.io

Class CounterOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • java.io.FilterOutputStream
        • xxl.core.io.CounterOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable

    public class CounterOutputStream
extends FilterOutputStream
    This class provides a decorator for an output stream that counts the number of bytes that are written to the underlying stream.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      protected long counter
      The int value counter stores the number of bytes written to the underlying output stream.
